    <label>SOX Audit Trail</label>
    <protected>false</protected>
    <values>
        <field>Framework__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">SOX</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Policy_Description__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Sarbanes-Oxley Act Section 404 requires organizations to maintain audit trails for all financial reporting processes. Setup Audit Trail and Field History Tracking must be enabled and retained for a minimum of 7 years for public companies.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Legal_Citation__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">Sarbanes-Oxley Act Section 404 - Management Assessment of Internal Controls</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Remediation_Steps__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:string">1. Enable Setup Audit Trail with 7-year retention period.
2. Enable Field History Tracking on all financial objects.
3. Export audit trail data quarterly for long-term storage.
4. Implement automated audit trail monitoring and alerting.
5. Document audit trail retention and archival procedures.</value>
    </values>
    <values>
        <field>Risk_Weight__c</field>
        <value xsi:type="xsd:double">9.0</value>
    </values>
